TTY detection uses os.Stdout.Stat() and checks (mode &amp; os.ModeCharDevice) != 0. This is the stdlib-only test; golang.org/x/term is NOT used (preserves <ref spec="principles.zero_dependency_portable">zero dependency</ref>). NO_COLOR is honored per https://no-color.org/: any non-empty value disables color when set, unless explicitly overridden by --color=always. See <ref spec="output.flag_precedence">flag precedence</ref>.